		<title type="html"><![CDATA[Micro help on DHT]]></title>
		<link rel="alternate" href="http://forum.bittorrent-archive.mythra.dev/viewtopic.php?id=416&amp;action=new"/>
		<summary type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Developer can send to other client query</p><p>Query:<br /></p><div class="codebox"><pre><code>q = &quot;help&quot;
a.path = &quot;a.name&quot;</code></pre></div><p>Response:<br /></p><div class="codebox"><pre><code>r.help = &quot;name of torrent&quot;</code></pre></div><p>Query:<br /></p><div class="codebox"><pre><code>q = &quot;help&quot;
a.path = &quot;q&quot;</code></pre></div><p>Response:</p><div class="codebox"><pre><code>r.help = &quot;q=[help, ping, find_node, get_peers,  announce_peer]
help - Micro help about new parameter of dht packet.
 a.path (query packet) - path to new parameter
 r.help (responce packet) - help about new parameter

more: http://forum.bittorrent-archive.mythra.dev/viewtopic.php?pid=2134

other see on http://bittorrent.org/beps/bep_0005.html&quot;</code></pre></div>]]></summary>
